Subject: drm/amd/display: support new PMFW interface to disable Z9 only
Git-commit: b4c55e525461a9a091421e952d1e052127d558a8
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: jsc#PED-1166 jsc#PED-1168 jsc#PED-1170 jsc#PED-1218 jsc#PED-1220 jsc#PED-1222 jsc#PED-1223 jsc#PED-1225

[Why]
Need to disable Z9 on configurations that only support Z10

[How]
Support new PMFW interface to disable Z9

Reviewed-by: Nicholas Kazlauskas <Nicholas.Kazlauskas@amd.com>
Acked-by: Rodrigo Siqueira <Rodrigo.Siqueira@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Eric Yang <Eric.Yang2@amd.com>
Tested-by: Daniel Wheeler <daniel.wheeler@amd.com>
